member.name: CRYPT_DEFAULT_CONTEXT_MULTI_OID_PARA
member.summary: The CRYPT_DEFAULT_CONTEXT_MULTI_OID_PARA structure is used with the function to contain an array of object identifier strings.

member.name: CRYPT_DEFAULT_CONTEXT_MULTI_OID_PARA.cOID
member.summary: The number of elements in the rgpszOID array.

member.name: CRYPT_DEFAULT_CONTEXT_MULTI_OID_PARA.rgpszOID
member.summary: An array of pointers to null-terminated ANSI strings that contain the object identifier strings of the certificate signature algorithm to install the default provider for, for example, szOID_OIWSEC_md5RSA. The cOID member of this structure contains the number of elements in this array.
